citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:50 pm on
04/12/2016. Outside door leading to the facility was closed and locked. Attempted to contact registrant by phone
and left message. Left a business card on the door with inspectors contact information and departed the facility.

ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:50 pm on
04/12/2016.  Outside door leading to the facility was closed and locked.  Attempted to contact registrant by phone
and left message.  Left a business card on the door with inspectors contact information and departed the facility.
